original: Lundgren, Ernst Eric Helge, direktör, Linköping, f. 26/3/02 i Stora Mel-lösa, Örebro 1., av riksdagsman Ernst o. Alma Lundgren. —■ Chef f. samt innehav, av Svensk Fastighetsförmedling m. huvudkont. i Linköp. o. sextio avd :kont. över hela landet. Medl. av KAK, KDAK, KNA. Hobby: smalfilmning.
translated:
Lundgren, Ernst Eric Helge, director, Linköping, b. 26/3/02 in Stora Mellösa, Örebro 1st district, son of parliament member Ernst and Alma Lundgren. —■ Head of and holder of Svensk Fastighetsförmedling with headquarters in Linköping and sixty branches across the country. Member of KAK, KDAK, KNA. Hobby: filming with small format films.

Note: "\d\d m. partner's name" implies marriage in the year 19xx.
